CREATE TABLE PMIS_ADM.NKPD(NKPDID number NOT NULL,
                           NKPDParentID number,
                           NKPDCode varchar2(20),
                           NKPDName varchar2(500),
                           NKPDNickname varchar2(500),
                           IsActive number(1) CHECK (IsActive BETWEEN 0 AND 1)
                          );

ALTER TABLE PMIS_ADM.NKPD ADD CONSTRAINT NKPD_PK PRIMARY KEY (NKPDID);
ALTER TABLE PMIS_ADM.NKPD ADD CONSTRAINT NKPD_NKPDParent_FK FOREIGN KEY (NKPDParentID) REFERENCES PMIS_ADM.NKPD (NKPDID);
ALTER TABLE PMIS_ADM.NKPD ADD CONSTRAINT NKPDCode_UNQ UNIQUE (NKPDCode);

CREATE SEQUENCE PMIS_ADM.NKPD_ID_SEQ
START WITH 1 
INCREMENT BY 1 
NOMAXVALUE;

CREATE TRIGGER PMIS_ADM.TRG_NKPD_INSERT
BEFORE INSERT ON PMIS_ADM.NKPD
FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
   SELECT PMIS_ADM.NKPD_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :new.NKPDID FROM dual;
END;
/
